result.name: 新發粥店

reviews.text:
Very very small and down to earth place.
Very good quality of food

This place has been here for a long time. I used to come here to pick up breakfast before heading to school as a kid in the early 90's. I haven't been here for at least that long, but the taste is exactly as I remembered it.

Good and quality food on the cheap, which is how us Chinese like our food. Just make sure you have someone that can read/speak Cantonese, or it will be hard to order what you want.
I support traditional congee because taste better.
cheap, fast, tasty!
This congee shop has been around for decades. I like the taste of the congee there and the fried noodles are a must-try.

result.name: 新發粥店

reviews.text: 在銅鑼灣鵝頸橋侧。裝修普通。舖內雜物多。坐不舒股。粥尚合格。腸粉。油條。没大吸引力。。。很平凡。。。
價錢超值，味道亦不錯，係銅鑼灣，一碗粥，一碟炸兩，只需32元，邊到搵！
艇仔粥冇豬皮豆粉水，蝦米腸超難食，垃圾！
粥料都多，但味道一般，話就話拉布腸粉，但一啲都唔滑，係我食過最難食的腸粉，可能因為價格比較低原估，地方污糟，員工剝皮蛋掉在地上，洗完放返落去。
鬧市中的傳統平價粥檔，屹立銅鑼灣數十年，價錢大衆化！陳舊的装修，不嫌地方小可以一試！
